      <title>日本通胀超出预期，负利率结束仍遥遥无期</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/japans-inflation-beats-forecasts-end-negative-rates-still-sight-2024-02-27/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本 1 月份核心消费者通胀连续第三个月放缓，但超出了预期，并维持在央行 2% 的目标水平，使日本将在 4 月份结束负利率的预期继续存在。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/japans-inflation-beats-forecasts-end-negative-rates-still-sight-2024-02-27/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 00:22:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
